        protected Map<String,String> generateNamespaceMappings(List inputs)
                                                throws UnknownOperationException,
                                                       IOException
        Generates a map of all the namespaces for the operation and all of the types required to call the operation. Namesspace prefixes (the key) start with ns1 representing the operation, and continue incrementally for all additional namespaces (ns2, ns3 ... etc).
